div.ab:




He did not write me any news as he himself used to do.


] So, neither he sent a letter nor even left any traces behind him.


] But he also went out with nothing. It is the was (i.e. he took the way of the mystics).


Therefore, I] feel sory, O father, for your condition.


] There is nothing in this case. Write to me about your news


] And the mysteries of this later, if Allah wills.


] May he fulfill His loving kindness unto you, and may He increase His bounty unto you. Your obedient.
